CatDescriptText: A shoe shine "menu" is visible through the window displaying choices for tan, black, suede, suede & leather, white, white & black, and white & tan.  There is a fire hydrant on the street corner with B and 18 stenciled on it.
TitMainTitle: Exterior of small one story brick shoe shine parlor with advertisements on outside for Lucky Strikes, Camels, and Pall Mall cigarettes and fire hydrant in front
